data.description: ***LEASE-PURCHASE IS AVAILABLE FOR THIS PROPERTY***  Welcome to your private home in the country ! Awesome ranch home with room to enjoy the outdoors. +/- 4.23 acres with creek frontage, freshly planted landscaping, & a small fruit orchard with apple & pear trees, and a private well for gardening. The creek area is cleared and ready for your outdoor area or campsite. 2 beds & 1 bath on the main level with new paint & lighting and the basement features a full in law/teen suite with 1 bed room, 1 full bath, living room, dining room, full kitchen, & a private entry. 220v power located at the basement entry for hot tub installation. This could also be rented out for extra income ! New HVAC & air ducts with an air scrubber installed in 2022, metal roof less than 6 years old, complete ADT security system on all windows & doors, glass break, motion sensors, & cameras. Septic was pumped in 2021. Long, private driveway with gated entry. Come make an offer while this one is still available !
